        {
          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "id": "gallery_character12737",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/09/05/2868fbf7148ccc04e1c5a36e9ca5717d_6091100740016137488.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>In Solid Phlogiston Nail challenges, you must <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">break Engraved Stone Pillars </span>and collect the <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">inscription's power </span>stored within to repair the Iridescent Inscriptions and cause the floating Solid Phlogiston Nail to plunge back into the ground.<br>The more you collect, the more you further the Iridescent Inscriptions' repairs.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/3"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character19340",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/09/05/6bba5db2a14385b35fab6c04437a4a8d_8065494840195506723.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>However, the <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">dark power</span> trapped beneath these Solid Phlogiston Nails will oppose the Inscriptions' repair.<br>Collect enough power to complete the repairs before the darkness overwhelms the entire process.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/3"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character35345",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/09/05/ddb68850b0c2320c8d120fa27a514628_4720182559384020798.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>The conflict between an Inscription's power and the darkness is so fierce that it can change the terrain, even producing Unstable Phlogiston Crystals that will <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">explode when you are nearby</span>, so stay vigilant as the challenge proceeds.</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/3"
              }
            ],
